{"tid":948140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"整容怪處女 vs 非處女","createTime":"2018-12-19T21:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T23:51:53.000Z","uid":180913,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62d7f75bcbf90c3298ebb9d5f3394681cc1fb78a","tid":948140,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:16:40.000Z","msg":"假設教育背景身材性格一樣<br />\n如果做老婆 整容處女（ 雙眼皮加打針）定係 非處女？<br />\n<br />\n整容嘅人根本就唔知 點戀愛，深知對方只係中意個醫生作品，唔係本身既你<br />\n<br />\n而 非處女 會令到個男人 意識到呢個女人 有吸引男人嘅價值會更加 愛錫佢<br />\n同埋 拍拖可以令一個女人更加明白一個男人所需<br />\n<br />\n如果我係男人<br />\n我寧願要 非處女做老婆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果要 感受真愛，記得唔好開 第一刀<br />\n因為係男人都會介意<br />\n<br />\n就好似一樣袋二手永遠高價過俾人界花左<br />\n無人想要，理得你入面幾 乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2bb4f07f1cf96ff7f3bc818c150c6eae652bfd","tid":948140,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:20:50.000Z","msg":"負評  整容怪處女<br />\n正評  非處女"},{"pid":"ab5be341360a2999772bf448d07412f902ee7a0c","tid":948140,"uid":178228,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:22:39.000Z","msg":"整得容既格 點會係處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3305fa2b41f9492c3e7163d3dd5dc4b96771afd8","tid":948140,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab5be341360a2999772bf448d07412f902ee7a0c","tid":948140,"uid":178228,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:22:39.000Z","msg":"整得容既格 點會係處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:24:38.000Z","msg":"兩樣嘢冇衝突㗎喎 <br />\n不過做完個樣會似唔係"},{"pid":"553bf0e3599cec9157fada568e9c4255567925aa","tid":948140,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab5be341360a2999772bf448d07412f902ee7a0c","tid":948140,"uid":178228,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:22:39.000Z","msg":"整得容既格 點會係處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:25:13.000Z","msg":"想知乜嘢叫整容格"},{"pid":"59fd7b05c1cd34a75fe7618cc1a7f267181577a7","tid":948140,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:49:44.000Z","msg":"睇下塊處係咪整返黎"},{"pid":"7ebffd20d557c0565369e7e6f804f5da9190beec","tid":948140,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T23:51:53.000Z","msg":"唔知樓主係用d 咩方式可以好環保咁上網呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做狗都唔會以污染自己個狗竇為榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/235946_3a065c14cc2bcbd4eb03bcdd77991318.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F235946_3a065c14cc2bcbd4eb03bcdd77991318.png&h=7be82773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/192852_c55bfca827914b85e2237a7b04a13847.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F192852_c55bfca827914b85e2237a7b04a13847.png&h=8b68fed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MoYXFQ6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoYXFQ6.png&h=216310d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n改名都無撚用<br />\n<br />\n麻煩其他人copy 番俾樓主睇，佢block 左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}